						               													<description>The Legends of Crimson Bluff is an deck-destruction fighting game that puts players as actors in the roles of rival gunfighters, gamblers and outlaws in the American Old West. Each has a unique deck of cards representing their skills, signature moves, etc. Cards are multi-purpose, so players must decide the best use for each situation.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players collectively select a scene before each game. Scene decks can be team-based struggles or free-for-all brawls, and cards add additional props, minor characters, rules and objectives.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;As gunfighters take wounds, they lose cards from their decks until they become stricken. Stricken gunfighters continue to fight, but can be ignored as a target by other players. Be the player or team to fulfill the scene objective to win!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
